  "title": "A Zeltron's Trandoshan Troubles",
  "summary": "On Trandosha, the Caspian Presav Crestian Tarasar tours old Sith ruins in his capacity as Executive Director of the charity The Mission, accompanied by the Sith-uniformed Captain Drorq. He stumbles upon the disreputable Zeltron smuggler Ezlo being marched off by two Trandoshan guards who accuse him of defecating in a ceremonial fountain. Crestian intervenes with smooth diplomacy and talks the guards into releasing Ezlo into his custody, just as two of Darth Malign's Dark Side agents, Aldus Syn and Carmella Rise, emerge from a hidden passage carrying stolen Sith data chips. After a tense, politically charged exchange in which Crestian needles Aldus over protocol, the Sith agents depart, vowing to report Ezlo's desecration of Malign's former seat of power. Crestian extracts a favor owed from the oblivious, spice-peddling Ezlo before the comic encounter winds down.",
